      "content": "that's one way to look at it, but i don't feel \"valued.\" i feel watched. honestly, now that i'm in this office, it feels like every move i make is being documented. like they didn't give me the office to reward me, they did it so they can keep the most \"difficult\" person in a glass box where they can see everything. does that sound crazy?",
